{"tid":125052,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"穿著「習包子」T恤 留美中國學生被控顛覆國家","createTime":"2017-02-18T06:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T16:58:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0fb33d72d19a3af9ee8704a2214f5c7e74690383","tid":125052,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phph139Mo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phph139Mo.jpg&h=67102bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國留美學生權平，在返國後穿出印有「習包子」的衣服上街，最後被當局逮捕。（圖擷自推特）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國29歲留美學生權平，去年8月底在返國後穿著印有「#XITLER #習包子 #大撒幣」的T恤走上街頭，暗諷習近平是「習特勒、大傻B」，最後他被中國當局逮捕，並以「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」起訴<br />\n<br />\n據《法國國際廣播電台》報導，權平衣服上的文字除了以諧音嘲諷習近平之外，「大撒幣」同時也是在諷刺習所推動的金錢外交。權平在PO出照片後，更宣稱自己要在10月1日國慶日穿上這件衣服，走上街頭遊行，結果在國慶日前夕他就遭官方逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n權平在美國的朋友古懿當時收到了一封緊急訊息，裡頭寫著「出事了」，隨後便無法聯絡上對方。親友們連忙四處奔走並呼籲中國釋放權平，但權平現在已被起訴意圖煽動顛覆國家，並且沒有辦法與辯護律師會面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1978871\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1978871&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2BhzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=d1c5cb36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1978871&h=12ff415f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1978871</a>"},{"pid":"94a2f5845c8fcd503180b60dbd134ed367ce4685","tid":125052,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:53:48.000Z","msg":"傻逼"},{"pid":"cc6ae4d555e793a32d085222810837842183e3cb","tid":125052,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc666e0fe2ec5dc38c83309744b4789d35bd335b","tid":125052,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"